'''桑人'''（'''San'''）或'''薩恩人'''（'''Saan'''）、'''巴薩爾瓦人'''（'''Basarwa'''） ，是生活於[[南非|南非]]、[[博茨瓦納|博茨瓦納]]、[[納米比亞|納米比亞]]與[[安哥拉|安哥拉]]的一個以[[狩獵採集|狩獵採集]]為生[[原住民族|原住民族]]。生活在不同地區的桑人的語言差異極大<ref name=Barnard>{{cite book|last=Barnard|first=Alan|title=Anthropology and the Bushman|year=2007|publisher=Berg|location=Oxford|isbn=9781847883308|pages=4–7|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=e3MihaaJ314C|access-date=2014-05-28|archive-date=2015-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150320202522/http://books.google.com/books?id=e3MihaaJ314C|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Who are the San? – San Map (Click on the image to enlarge)|url=http://www.wim-sa.org/about-the-san/who-are-the-san|publisher=WIMSA|accessdate=13 January 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140113052634/http://www.wim-sa.org/about-the-san/who-are-the-san|archivedate=2014年1月13日}}</ref>，桑人也常被外人称作'''布须曼人'''（{{lang-en|Bushmen}}，意为“丛林人”），但这被认为是一种贬损的称呼。

自1950年代開始，桑人社會開始進行現代化。此外，[[遺傳學|遺傳學]]上根據[[人類Y染色體DNA單倍型類群|人類Y染色體DNA單倍型類群]]的研究顯示，此民族可能是世界上現存最古老的民族之一<ref>Spencer Wells (2003). ''The Journey of Man''. ISBN 069111532X. Pg. 56-58</ref>。2009年的一項非洲人基因多樣性調查顯示，桑人是非洲基因最多樣的五個民族之一<ref>{{cite news|last=Connor|first=Steve|title=World's most ancient race traced in DNA study|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/science/worlds-most-ancient-race-traced-in-dna-study-1677113.html|accessdate=19 January 2014|newspaper=The Independent|date=1 May 2009|archive-date=2014-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203161751/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/science/worlds-most-ancient-race-traced-in-dna-study-1677113.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Gill>{{cite news |author=Gill, Victoria |date=1 May 2009 |title=Africa's genetic secrets unlocked |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/8027269.stm |format=online edition |work=BBC World News |publisher=[[BBC|British Broadcasting Corporation]] |accessdate=2009-09-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090701001654/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/8027269.stm |archivedate=2009年7月1日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=The Genetic Structure and History of Africans and African Americans|journal=Science|date=2009-05-22|doi=10.1126/science.1172257|url=http://science.sciencemag.org/content/324/5930/1035|language=en|volume=324|issue=5930|pages=1035–1044|issn=0036-8075|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Sarah A. Tishkoff, Floyd A. Reed, Françoise R. Friedlaender, Christopher Ehret, Alessia Ranciaro, Alain Froment, Jibril B. Hirbo, Agnes A. Awomoyi, Jean-Marie Bodo, Ogobara Doumbo, Muntaser Ibrahim, Abdalla T. Juma, Maritha J. Kotze, Godfrey Lema, Jason H. Moore, Holly Mortensen, Thomas B. Nyambo, Sabah A. Omar, Kweli Powell, Gideon S. Pretorius, Michael W. Smith, Mahamadou A. Thera, Charles Wambebe, James L. Weber, Scott M. Williams|archive-date=2021-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312043848/https://science.sciencemag.org/content/324/5930/1035|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

